\mt2 This book contains the account of Nehemiah supervising the rebuilding of the walls of Jerusalem and of teaching the people the laws that God wanted them to obey. We call this book  
\mt1 Nehemiah  
\c 1  
\s1 Nehemiah’s prayer  
\p
\v 1  \add I am\add* \w Nehemiah|strong="H5166"\w*, \w the|strong="H1697"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Hacaliah|strong="H2446"\w*. \add I am writing\add* \w this|strong="H1697"\w* \w account|strong="H1697"\w* \add of what I did when I returned to Jerusalem. After King Artaxerxes had been ruling the Persian Empire\add* \w for|strong="H1121"\w* almost 20 \w years|strong="H8141"\w*, near \w the|strong="H1697"\w* end \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w that|strong="H1697"\w* \w year|strong="H8141"\w*, \w I|strong="H1697"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H8141"\w* \w Susa|strong="H7800"\w*, \w the|strong="H1697"\w* capital \add of Persia\add*.   
\p
\v 2 \w My|strong="H5921"\w* brother \w Hanani|strong="H2607"\w* \w came|strong="H3063"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* visit \w me|strong="H5921"\w*. \w He|strong="H1931"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w some|strong="H4480"\w* other men \w had|strong="H3063"\w* just \w returned|strong="H3064"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w*. \w I|strong="H5921"\w* queried \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jews|strong="H3064"\w* \w who|strong="H1931"\w* \w were|strong="H3063"\w* living \w there|strong="H4480"\w*, \w whose|strong="H3064"\w* \add parents\add* \w had|strong="H3063"\w* been ◄exiled/\w taken|strong="H7628"\w* forcefully► \add to Babylonia many years previously\add*. \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w also|strong="H1931"\w* \w asked|strong="H7592"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \add what was happening in\add* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w*.   
\p
\v 3 \w They|strong="H8033"\w* said \w to|strong="H3389"\w* \w me|strong="H4480"\w*, “\w The|strong="H4480"\w* Jews \w in|strong="H7604"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w* \w who|strong="H7604"\w* returned \w there|strong="H8033"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* Babylonia \w are|strong="H8179"\w* living \w in|strong="H7604"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H1419"\w* \w difficult|strong="H1419"\w* situation. \w The|strong="H4480"\w* \w walls|strong="H2346"\w* \w of|strong="H8179"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w* \w have|strong="H3389"\w* been \w broken|strong="H6555"\w* \w down|strong="H6555"\w*, \w and|strong="H1419"\w* even \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w* \w gates|strong="H8179"\w* \w have|strong="H3389"\w* been \w burned|strong="H3341"\w* \w down|strong="H6555"\w*.”   
\p
\v 4 \w When|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w*, \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w sat|strong="H3427"\w* \w down|strong="H3427"\w* \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w cried|strong="H1058"\w*. \w For|strong="H6440"\w* several \w days|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w mourned|strong="H1058"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* ◄\w fasted|strong="H6684"\w*/abstained \w from|strong="H6440"\w* eating food►, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w prayed|strong="H6419"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w our|strong="H8085"\w* \w God|strong="H8064"\w*, \add who is/rules\add* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8064"\w*.  
\v 5 \w I|strong="H3068"\w* said, “\w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \add you who are/rule\add* \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8064"\w*, \w you|strong="H3372"\w* \w are|strong="H8064"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wonderful \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w awesome|strong="H3372"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*. \w You|strong="H3372"\w* \w keep|strong="H8104"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w promise|strong="H1285"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w faithfully|strong="H2617"\w* \w love|strong="H2617"\w* those \w who|strong="H3068"\w* \w love|strong="H2617"\w* \w you|strong="H3372"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w who|strong="H3068"\w* \w obey|strong="H8104"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w commands|strong="H4687"\w*.  
\v 6 \w Now|strong="H4994"\w* \w please|strong="H4994"\w* \w look|strong="H5869"\w* \w down|strong="H6440"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w listen|strong="H8085"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w what|strong="H8085"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w am|strong="H1961"\w* \w praying|strong="H6419"\w*. \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w pray|strong="H6419"\w* \w during|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w day|strong="H3117"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w night|strong="H3915"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H1121"\w*. \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w confess|strong="H3034"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w sinned|strong="H2398"\w*. \w Even|strong="H5869"\w* \w my|strong="H8085"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w sinned|strong="H2398"\w* \w against|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*.  
\v 7 We \w have|strong="H5650"\w* \w acted|strong="H2254"\w* \w very|strong="H2254"\w* wickedly. \add Many years ago\add* \w your|strong="H8104"\w* \w servant|strong="H5650"\w* \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w* \w gave|strong="H6680"\w* us \w your|strong="H8104"\w* \w laws|strong="H2706"\w* \w and|strong="H4872"\w* \w all|strong="H2254"\w* \w the|strong="H8104"\w* \w things|strong="H4687"\w* \w you|strong="H6680"\w* \w commanded|strong="H6680"\w* us \w to|strong="H8104"\w* \w do|strong="H8104"\w* [DOU], \w but|strong="H3808"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H5650"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w obeyed|strong="H8104"\w*/done \w them|strong="H6680"\w*.   
\p
\v 8 “\w But|strong="H5971"\w* \w please|strong="H4994"\w* \w remember|strong="H2142"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w you|strong="H6680"\w* \w told|strong="H6680"\w* \w your|strong="H6680"\w* \w servant|strong="H5650"\w* \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w*. \w You|strong="H6680"\w* \w said|strong="H1697"\w*, ‘If \w you|strong="H6680"\w* sin, \w I|strong="H1697"\w* \w will|strong="H5971"\w* \w scatter|strong="H6327"\w* \w you|strong="H6680"\w* \w among|strong="H5971"\w* \w the|strong="H6680"\w* ◄\add heathen nations/nations that do not believe in me\add*►.  
\v 9 \w But|strong="H1961"\w* \w if|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w return|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w* \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w obey|strong="H6213"\w* \w my|strong="H8104"\w* \w commands|strong="H4687"\w*, \w even|strong="H6213"\w* \w if|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w been|strong="H1961"\w* exiled \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w very|strong="H6213"\w* \w remote|strong="H7097"\w*/distant \w places|strong="H4725"\w* \w on|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*, \w I|strong="H6213"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w bring|strong="H7725"\w* \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w here|strong="H8033"\w* \add to Israel\add*, \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w land|strong="H4725"\w* \w that|strong="H6213"\w* \w I|strong="H6213"\w* [MTY] \w have|strong="H1961"\w* chosen \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* honored \w in|strong="H6213"\w*.’   
\p
\v 10 “We \w are|strong="H1992"\w* \w your|strong="H3027"\w* \w servants|strong="H5650"\w*. We \w are|strong="H1992"\w* \w the|strong="H3027"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w whom|strong="H1992"\w* \w you|strong="H3027"\w* \w brought|strong="H5650"\w* here \w by|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H3027"\w* \w very|strong="H1419"\w* \w great|strong="H1419"\w* \w power|strong="H3027"\w* [MTY, DOU]  
\v 11 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w please|strong="H4994"\w* hear \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \w prayer|strong="H8605"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w mine|strong="H5414"\w*, \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w prayers|strong="H8605"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w all|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* people \w who|strong="H5650"\w* \w are|strong="H3117"\w* delighted \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w revere|strong="H3372"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* [MTY]. \w Today|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w go|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*, \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w request|strong="H6440"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w he|strong="H3117"\w* \w do|strong="H4994"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w great|strong="H6440"\w* \w favor|strong="H6440"\w*. \w Please|strong="H4994"\w* motivate \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w act|strong="H4994"\w* \w kindly|strong="H6440"\w* \w toward|strong="H6440"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w in|strong="H4428"\w* order \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w successful|strong="H6743"\w* \add in obtaining what I want\add*.”  
\p \w At|strong="H3117"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w time|strong="H3117"\w*, \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w was|strong="H8034"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w one|strong="H2088"\w* \w whose|strong="H5650"\w* \w work|strong="H5414"\w* \w was|strong="H8034"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* taste \w all|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* food \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w drink|strong="H4945"\w* \w before|strong="H6440"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w was|strong="H8034"\w* \w served|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*, \add to be sure that no one had put poison in it\add*.   
\c 2  
\s1 Artaxerses allowed Nehemiah to go to Jerusalem  
\p
\v 1 \w After|strong="H1961"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w* Artaxerxes \add had been ruling the Persian Empire\add* \w for|strong="H6440"\w* almost 20 \w years|strong="H8141"\w*, ◄\w during|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* spring/\w before|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* hot season► \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w year|strong="H8141"\w*, \w when|strong="H1961"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w time|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w serve|strong="H1961"\w* \w wine|strong="H3196"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \add during a feast\add*, \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w took|strong="H5375"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w wine|strong="H3196"\w* \w and|strong="H6242"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w*. \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w never|strong="H3808"\w* \w looked|strong="H5375"\w* \w sad|strong="H7451"\w* \w when|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H8141"\w* \w front|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w before|strong="H6440"\w*, \add but on that day he saw that I looked very sad\add*.  
\v 2 \w So|strong="H3966"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w asked|strong="H2470"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*, “\w Why|strong="H4069"\w* \w are|strong="H4428"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w sad|strong="H7451"\w*? \add I know that\add* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H4428"\w* \w not|strong="H2088"\w* \w sick|strong="H2470"\w*. \w It|strong="H3588"\w* must \w be|strong="H3820"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H4428"\w* \w troubled|strong="H3966"\w* \w about|strong="H4428"\w* something.” \w Then|strong="H2088"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w was|strong="H3820"\w* \w very|strong="H3966"\w* \w afraid|strong="H3372"\w*, \add because it was not proper to be sad when I came to the king\add* (\w OR|strong="H3068"\w*, \add because I was worried what the king would do to me if he refused to do what I was about to request him to do\add*).   
\p
\v 3 \w I|strong="H3808"\w* replied, “\w Your|strong="H6440"\w* majesty, \w I|strong="H3808"\w* hope \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H4428"\w* \w live|strong="H2421"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H7489"\w* \w long|strong="H5769"\w* \w time|strong="H5769"\w*! \w But|strong="H3808"\w* ◄\w how|strong="H4069"\w* \w can|strong="H3808"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* prevent myself \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w being|strong="H1004"\w* \w sad|strong="H7489"\w*, \w because|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \w where|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H6440"\w* ancestors \w are|strong="H5892"\w* buried \add has been destroyed\add* \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w is|strong="H4428"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w ruins|strong="H5892"\w*?/\w I|strong="H3808"\w* \w cannot|strong="H3808"\w* \w keep|strong="H2421"\w* myself \w from|strong="H6440"\w* looking \w sad|strong="H7489"\w*, \w because|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \w where|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H6440"\w* ancestors \w are|strong="H5892"\w* buried \add has been destroyed and\add* \w is|strong="H4428"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w ruins|strong="H5892"\w*.► [RHQ] \add Even\add* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \w gates|strong="H8179"\w* \w have|strong="H1004"\w* \w been|strong="H5769"\w* completely burned.”   
\p
\v 4 \w The|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* replied, “\w What|strong="H4100"\w* \w do|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w want|strong="H1245"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w do|strong="H4100"\w* \add for you\add*?”  
\p \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w prayed|strong="H6419"\w* \add silently\add* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w our|strong="H5921"\w* \w God|strong="H8064"\w* \add who is/rules\add* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w heaven|strong="H8064"\w*.  
\v 5 \w Then|strong="H7971"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* replied, “If \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w are|strong="H5892"\w* willing \add to do it\add*, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* if \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H5650"\w* \w pleased|strong="H3190"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*, \w send|strong="H7971"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H7971"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w* \add of Jerusalem\add* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \add province\add* \w where|strong="H5921"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* ancestors \w are|strong="H5892"\w* buried, \w in|strong="H5921"\w* order \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w may|strong="H4428"\w* \add help people to\add* \w rebuild|strong="H1129"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w*.”   
\p
\v 6 \w While|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w queen|strong="H7694"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w sitting|strong="H3427"\w* \w beside|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*, \w he|strong="H5704"\w* \w asked|strong="H7971"\w*, \add “If I allow you to go,\add* \w how|strong="H4970"\w* \w long|strong="H5704"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w gone|strong="H1961"\w*? \w When|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w return|strong="H7725"\w*?” \add I told the king how long I would be gone, and\add* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* \w permission|strong="H7971"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w go|strong="H7971"\w*, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* told \w him|strong="H5414"\w* what day \add I wanted to leave\add*.   
\p
\v 7 \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w also|strong="H4428"\w* said \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w*, “If \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w are|strong="H4428"\w* willing \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w do|strong="H2895"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w*, write letters \w for|strong="H5704"\w* \w me|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w take|strong="H5674"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w governors|strong="H6346"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* province \w west|strong="H5676"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \add Euphrates\add* \w River|strong="H5104"\w*. Tell \w them|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w allow|strong="H5414"\w* \w me|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w travel|strong="H5674"\w* safely \add through their province\add* \w until|strong="H5704"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* arrive \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w*.  
\v 8 \w Also|strong="H3027"\w*, \add please write\add* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* letter \w to|strong="H5921"\w* Asaph, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w man|strong="H2896"\w* \w who|strong="H8104"\w* \w takes|strong="H5414"\w* \w care|strong="H3027"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w forest|strong="H6508"\w* \add in that area\add*, telling \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w me|strong="H5414"\w* \w timber|strong="H6086"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w make|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w beams|strong="H7136"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w support|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w gates|strong="H8179"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w fortress|strong="H1002"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w is|strong="H3027"\w* \w near|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w temple|strong="H1004"\w*, \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w timber|strong="H6086"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w making|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w walls|strong="H2346"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w city|strong="H5892"\w*, \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* building \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w which|strong="H1004"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \add will live\add*.” \w The|strong="H5921"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w did|strong="H8104"\w* \w what|strong="H2896"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* requested \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w do|strong="H8104"\w*, \w because|strong="H5921"\w* \w my|strong="H8104"\w* \w God|strong="H5414"\w* \w was|strong="H5892"\w* \w graciously|strong="H2896"\w*/\w kindly|strong="H2896"\w* ◄helping/acting \w for|strong="H5921"\w*► \w me|strong="H5414"\w*.   
\p
\v 9  \add After I got ready, I left to travel to Judah\add*. \w The|strong="H5414"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w sent|strong="H7971"\w* some \w army|strong="H2428"\w* \w officers|strong="H8269"\w* \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w soldiers|strong="H2428"\w* riding \w on|strong="H7971"\w* \w horses|strong="H6571"\w* \w to|strong="H7971"\w* accompany \w me|strong="H5414"\w*, \add to protect me\add*. \w When|strong="H7971"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w came|strong="H4428"\w* \w to|strong="H7971"\w* where \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w governors|strong="H6346"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* provinces \w west|strong="H5676"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \add Euphrates\add* \w River|strong="H5104"\w* lived, \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* letters \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w king|strong="H4428"\w* \w had|strong="H4428"\w* written.   
\p
\v 10 \w But|strong="H8085"\w* \w when|strong="H8085"\w* \add two government officials,\add* \w Sanballat|strong="H5571"\w* \w from|strong="H3478"\w* \add a village near\add* Horon \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w Tobiah|strong="H2900"\w* \w from|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w Ammon|strong="H5984"\w* \add people-group\add*, \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w that|strong="H8085"\w* \w I|strong="H5650"\w* \w had|strong="H3478"\w* arrived, \w they|strong="H1992"\w* \w were|strong="H3478"\w* \w very|strong="H1419"\w* angry \w that|strong="H8085"\w* someone \w had|strong="H3478"\w* \w come|strong="H3478"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* help \w the|strong="H8085"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H1121"\w*.   
\s1 Nehemiah inspected the walls of Jerusalem  
\p
\v 11-12 When I arrived in Jerusalem, I did not tell anyone what thoughts God had given to me about what I should do there. Three days after I arrived in Jerusalem, I went out of the city in the evening, taking \w a|strong="H3068"\w* few other men with me. I was riding \w a|strong="H3068"\w* donkey; \w we|strong="H3068"\w* had no other animals with us.   
\p
\v 13 We \w left|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w*, \w going|strong="H3318"\w* \w out|strong="H3318"\w* \w through|strong="H6555"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w Valley|strong="H1516"\w* \w Gate|strong="H8179"\w*, \w then|strong="H1961"\w* \w past|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w well|strong="H5869"\w* called \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Jackal (\w OR|strong="H3068"\w*, \w Dragon|strong="H8577"\w*’s) \w Well|strong="H5869"\w*, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w then|strong="H1961"\w* \w past|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w gate|strong="H8179"\w* called \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Rubbish/Garbage \w Gate|strong="H8179"\w*. We \w inspected|strong="H7663"\w* \w all|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w walls|strong="H2346"\w* \w that|strong="H5869"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w been|strong="H1961"\w* \w broken|strong="H6555"\w* \w down|strong="H6555"\w* \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w all|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w gates|strong="H8179"\w* \w that|strong="H5869"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w been|strong="H1961"\w* burned \w down|strong="H6555"\w*.  
\v 14 \w Then|strong="H5674"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w went|strong="H5674"\w* \w to|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H8478"\w* \w Fountain|strong="H5869"\w* \w Gate|strong="H8179"\w* \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w to|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H8478"\w* \w pool|strong="H1295"\w* called \w the|strong="H8478"\w* \w King|strong="H4428"\w*’s \w Pool|strong="H1295"\w*, \w but|strong="H4428"\w* \w my|strong="H5674"\w* donkey could \w not|strong="H5674"\w* get \w through|strong="H5674"\w* \add the narrow opening\add* (\w OR|strong="H3068"\w*, \add the rubble\add*).  
\v 15 \w So|strong="H1961"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w turned|strong="H7725"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w went|strong="H5927"\w* along \w the|strong="H7725"\w* \add Kidron\add* \w Valley|strong="H1516"\w*. \w We|strong="H7725"\w* \w inspected|strong="H7663"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w before|strong="H1961"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w turned|strong="H7725"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w*/\w around|strong="H7725"\w* \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w entered|strong="H5927"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w* \w again|strong="H7725"\w* \w at|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* \w Valley|strong="H1516"\w* \w Gate|strong="H8179"\w*.  
\v 16 \w The|strong="H6213"\w* \add city\add* \w officials|strong="H5461"\w* \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w where|strong="H4100"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w had|strong="H3045"\w* \w gone|strong="H1980"\w* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w what|strong="H4100"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w was|strong="H3808"\w* \w doing|strong="H6213"\w*, \w because|strong="H3651"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w had|strong="H3045"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w told|strong="H5046"\w* anyone \w about|strong="H1980"\w* \w what|strong="H4100"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* planned \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w*. \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w had|strong="H3045"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w said|strong="H3651"\w* \w anything|strong="H4399"\w* \w about|strong="H1980"\w* \w it|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w Jewish|strong="H3064"\w* \w leaders|strong="H5461"\w* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w officials|strong="H5461"\w* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w priests|strong="H3548"\w* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w any|strong="H6213"\w* \w of|strong="H3548"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* others \w who|strong="H3548"\w* \w would|strong="H4100"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* helping \w me|strong="H5046"\w* \w in|strong="H1980"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w work|strong="H4399"\w* \add that I wanted to do\add*.   
\p
\v 17 \w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w now|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H7200"\w* said \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w them|strong="H7200"\w*, “\w You|strong="H3808"\w* \w all|strong="H7200"\w* know very well \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w terrible|strong="H7451"\w* \w things|strong="H7451"\w* \add that have happened to\add* \w our|strong="H7200"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w*. \w The|strong="H7200"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w* \w is|strong="H7451"\w* \w ruined|strong="H2717"\w*; \w even|strong="H5750"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w gates|strong="H8179"\w* \w are|strong="H8179"\w* \w burned|strong="H3341"\w* \w down|strong="H3341"\w*. \w So|strong="H1961"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* should \w rebuild|strong="H1129"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w city|strong="H8179"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w*. \w If|strong="H7200"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* do \w that|strong="H7200"\w*, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* \w longer|strong="H5750"\w* \w feel|strong="H7200"\w* humiliated/disgraced.”  
