\v 30 \w Next|strong="H8145"\w* \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w him|strong="H5048"\w*, \w Hananiah|strong="H2608"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Shelemiah|strong="H8018"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w Hanun|strong="H2586"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w sixth|strong="H8345"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Zalaph|strong="H6764"\w*, \w repaired|strong="H2388"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w section|strong="H4060"\w*. \w That|strong="H1121"\w* \w was|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w second|strong="H8145"\w* \add section that they repaired\add*. \w Next|strong="H8145"\w* \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w them|strong="H2388"\w*, \w Meshullam|strong="H4918"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Berekiah, \w made|strong="H2388"\w* \w repairs|strong="H2388"\w* across \w from|strong="H1121"\w* where \w he|strong="H1121"\w* lived.  
\v 31 Next \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w them|strong="H2388"\w*, \w Malchijah|strong="H4441"\w*, \w who|strong="H1121"\w* \w also|strong="H1121"\w* \w made|strong="H2388"\w* things \w from|strong="H1121"\w* gold, \w repaired|strong="H2388"\w* \add a section\add* \w as|strong="H5704"\w* \w far|strong="H5704"\w* \w as|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* building used \w by|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w temple|strong="H1004"\w* \w servants|strong="H5411"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w merchants|strong="H7402"\w*, \w which|strong="H1004"\w* \w was|strong="H1004"\w* close \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w Inspection|strong="H4663"\w* \w Gate|strong="H8179"\w*. \w This|strong="H1004"\w* \w was|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w gate|strong="H8179"\w* \w into|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w temple|strong="H1004"\w* \w that|strong="H1121"\w* \w was|strong="H1004"\w* \w near|strong="H5048"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* \w room|strong="H1004"\w* \w on|strong="H1004"\w* top \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* northeast \w corner|strong="H6438"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* wall.  
\v 32 Other \w men|strong="H2388"\w* \w who|strong="H6884"\w* \w made|strong="H2388"\w* things \w from|strong="H8179"\w* gold, along \w with|strong="H6629"\w* \w merchants|strong="H7402"\w*, \w repaired|strong="H2388"\w* \add the last section of the wall\add*, \w as|strong="H8179"\w* far \w as|strong="H8179"\w* \w the|strong="H2388"\w* \w Sheep|strong="H6629"\w* \w Gate|strong="H8179"\w*.   
\c 4  
\s1 Enemies opposed rebuilding the wall  
\p
\v 1 \w When|strong="H3588"\w* \w Sanballat|strong="H5571"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* rebuilding \w the|strong="H8085"\w* city \w wall|strong="H2346"\w*, \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w very|strong="H3966"\w* \w angry|strong="H2734"\w*. \w He|strong="H3588"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* enraged/\w furious|strong="H2734"\w*. \w He|strong="H3588"\w* \w made|strong="H6555"\w* fun \w of|strong="H2346"\w* \w us|strong="H3588"\w* Jews.  
\v 2 While \w his|strong="H3605"\w* colleagues \w and|strong="H3389"\w* officials \w of|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w army|strong="H3389"\w* \w troops|strong="H3898"\w* \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w had|strong="H3389"\w* come \w from|strong="H3389"\w* Samaria \w were|strong="H3605"\w* listening, \w he|strong="H6213"\w* said, “\w What|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w these|strong="H6213"\w* feeble/pathetic Jews \add think they\add* \w are|strong="H6213"\w* \w doing|strong="H6213"\w*? \w Do|strong="H6213"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* think \w that|strong="H3605"\w* if \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w offer|strong="H6213"\w* \w enough|strong="H3605"\w*/many sacrifices, \add their gods will hear them and enable\add* \w them|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* finish building \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wall \w in|strong="H6213"\w* \w one|strong="H3605"\w* day? \w The|strong="H3605"\w* stones \add that were in the wall previously have been weakened by\add* being burned \w in|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire. \w Those|strong="H3605"\w* stones \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w are|strong="H6213"\w* pulling \w out|strong="H6213"\w* \w of|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* rubbish/garbage heaps—\w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* think \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w they|strong="H6213"\w* \w can|strong="H6213"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w* strong again?” [RHQ]   
\p
\v 3 Tobiah \w was|strong="H6440"\w* \add standing\add* \w beside|strong="H5921"\w* Sanballat. \w He|strong="H5921"\w* said, “\w That|strong="H5975"\w* stone wall \add that they are building\add* \w is|strong="H6440"\w* very weak; \w so|strong="H5975"\w* if \w even|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fox climbed \w up|strong="H5975"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w*, \w the|strong="H6440"\w* wall would fall \w down|strong="H6440"\w*!”   
\p
\v 4 \w Then|strong="H3063"\w* \w I|strong="H3201"\w* prayed. \w I|strong="H3201"\w* said, “Our \w God|strong="H3808"\w*, hear us, because \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w are|strong="H3063"\w* ridiculing us! Cause \w the|strong="H1129"\w* words \w of|strong="H2346"\w* \w their|strong="H3808"\w* insults \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w fall|strong="H3782"\w* back \w on|strong="H7235"\w* \w them|strong="H1129"\w*! Allow \w their|strong="H3808"\w* enemies \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w come|strong="H3201"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* capture \w them|strong="H1129"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w force|strong="H3581"\w* \w them|strong="H1129"\w* \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w go|strong="H3201"\w* \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* foreign land!  
\v 5 \w They|strong="H3808"\w* \w are|strong="H3045"\w* guilty; \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w have|strong="H3045"\w* \add said things that\add* caused \w you|strong="H5704"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* angry \w while|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* \w here|strong="H5704"\w* \w who|strong="H6862"\w* \w are|strong="H3045"\w* building \w the|strong="H7200"\w* wall \w are|strong="H3045"\w* listening; \w so|strong="H3808"\w* punish \w them|strong="H7200"\w*!”   
\p
\v 6 \w But|strong="H1961"\w* \w after|strong="H5921"\w* \w some|strong="H3605"\w* \w time|strong="H6471"\w*, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* finished building \w the|strong="H3605"\w* wall \w around|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w whole|strong="H3605"\w* city, \w up|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* half \w as|strong="H1961"\w* high \w as|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* first wall \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w been|strong="H1961"\w*. \w We|strong="H3605"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* able \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w do|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w because|strong="H5921"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* worked very hard.   
\p
\v 7 \w But|strong="H5971"\w* \w when|strong="H5975"\w* Sanballat, Tobiah, \w the|strong="H5975"\w* \w men|strong="H5971"\w* \w from|strong="H5973"\w* Arabia, \w the|strong="H5975"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w from|strong="H5973"\w* \w the|strong="H5975"\w* Ammon \add people-group\add* \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w from|strong="H5973"\w* Ashdod \add city\add* heard \w that|strong="H5971"\w* \w the|strong="H5975"\w* work \w on|strong="H5975"\w* \w the|strong="H5975"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w* \w was|strong="H4725"\w* continuing \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w that|strong="H5971"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w were|strong="H5971"\w* filling \w in|strong="H5975"\w* \w the|strong="H5975"\w* gaps \w in|strong="H5975"\w* \w the|strong="H5975"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w*, \w they|strong="H5971"\w* became very angry.  
\v 8 \w They|strong="H5921"\w* \w all|strong="H7200"\w* planned \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w come|strong="H5971"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w fight|strong="H3898"\w* \w against|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Jerusalem [MTY] \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w cause|strong="H5971"\w* trouble.  
\v 9 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* prayed \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w our|strong="H3605"\w* God \add to protect us\add*, \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w put|strong="H7725"\w* \w men|strong="H3605"\w* \add around the walls\add* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* guard \add the city\add* day \w and|strong="H7725"\w* night.   
\p
\v 10 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w people|strong="H1931"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* [MTY] \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w started|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* say, “\w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w men|strong="H5288"\w* \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H3117"\w* \w working|strong="H6213"\w* \add on the wall\add* \w are|strong="H3117"\w* \w becoming|strong="H1961"\w* \w very|strong="H6213"\w* tired. \w There|strong="H1961"\w* \w is|strong="H1931"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \add heavy\add* rubble \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* must remove; \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w ourselves|strong="H2388"\w* \w cannot|strong="H4480"\w* finish \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w work|strong="H4399"\w*.   
\p
\v 11 “Besides, \w our|strong="H5375"\w* \w enemies|strong="H3027"\w* \w are|strong="H3027"\w* saying, ‘Before \w the|strong="H5375"\w* Jews see \w us|strong="H6213"\w*, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3027"\w* swoop \w down|strong="H3027"\w* \w on|strong="H3027"\w* \w them|strong="H3027"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* kill \w them|strong="H3027"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* stop \w their|strong="H5375"\w* \w work|strong="H4399"\w* \add on the wall\add*!’”   
\p
\v 12 \w The|strong="H5921"\w* Jews \w who|strong="H1129"\w* \w were|strong="H2719"\w* living \w near|strong="H5921"\w* \w our|strong="H5921"\w* enemies came \w and|strong="H2719"\w* told \w us|strong="H5921"\w* many times, “\w You|strong="H5921"\w* should leave \w the|strong="H5921"\w* city \w and|strong="H2719"\w* \w go|strong="H2719"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* other places, \w in|strong="H5921"\w* order \w that|strong="H2719"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* enemies \w will|strong="H2719"\w* not attack \w you|strong="H5921"\w*!”   
\p
\v 13 \w So|strong="H7235"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* put guards \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* places \w where|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w* \w was|strong="H2346"\w* \w not|strong="H5971"\w* \w very|strong="H7235"\w* \w high|strong="H7235"\w* \w yet|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* places \w where|strong="H5921"\w* there \w were|strong="H5971"\w* gaps \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w wall|strong="H2346"\w*. \w I|strong="H5921"\w* put guards \w to|strong="H5921"\w* protect \w each|strong="H5971"\w* \w of|strong="H2346"\w* \w their|strong="H5921"\w* family groups. \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w gave|strong="H7235"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* guards daggers, spears, \w and|strong="H5971"\w* bows \add and arrows\add*.  
\v 14 \w Then|strong="H8085"\w* after \w I|strong="H8085"\w* inspected everything, \w I|strong="H8085"\w* \w summoned|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* leaders \w and|strong="H6963"\w* \add other\add* officials \w and|strong="H6963"\w* \add many of\add* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* other \w people|strong="H8085"\w*, \w and|strong="H6963"\w* \w I|strong="H8085"\w* \w said|strong="H8085"\w* \w to|strong="H8085"\w* \w them|strong="H8085"\w*, “\w Do|strong="H8085"\w* \w not|strong="H8085"\w* \w be|strong="H6963"\w* afraid \w of|strong="H6963"\w* \w our|strong="H8085"\w* enemies! Think \w about|strong="H8085"\w* \add what\add* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, who \w is|strong="H4725"\w* great \w and|strong="H6963"\w* glorious, \add can do\add*! \w And|strong="H6963"\w* \w fight|strong="H3898"\w* \w to|strong="H8085"\w* protect \w your|strong="H8085"\w* friends, \w your|strong="H8085"\w* families, \w and|strong="H6963"\w* \w your|strong="H8085"\w* homes!”   
\p
\v 15 \w Our|strong="H3318"\w* enemies heard \w that|strong="H6213"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* knew \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w they|strong="H5704"\w* \w were|strong="H3318"\w* planning \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w and|strong="H2388"\w* \w that|strong="H6213"\w* God \w had|strong="H6213"\w* ◄spoiled \w their|strong="H2388"\w* \w plans|strong="H6213"\w*/prevented \w them|strong="H6213"\w* \w from|strong="H3318"\w* \w doing|strong="H6213"\w* \w what|strong="H6213"\w* \w they|strong="H5704"\w* planned►. \add But we were sure that God would defend us,\add* \w so|strong="H6213"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w started|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w work|strong="H4399"\w* \w on|strong="H4399"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* wall again.   
\p
\v 16 \w But|strong="H1961"\w* \w after|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H5971"\w*, \w only|strong="H1571"\w* \w half|strong="H8432"\w* \w of|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* \w men|strong="H5288"\w* \w who|strong="H1931"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* working \w for|strong="H3117"\w* \w me|strong="H1961"\w* \w worked|strong="H4399"\w* \w on|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H8432"\w* wall. \w The|strong="H8432"\w* \w others|strong="H5971"\w* \w stood|strong="H5971"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w on|strong="H3117"\w* \w guard|strong="H4929"\w*, holding \w their|strong="H8432"\w* spears, shields, bows \add and arrows\add*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \add wearing their\add* coats \w made|strong="H4399"\w* \w of|strong="H3117"\w* metal plates. \add To encourage the people\add*\w who|strong="H1931"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* building \w the|strong="H8432"\w* wall, \w their|strong="H8432"\w* leaders \w stood|strong="H5971"\w* behind \w them|strong="H8432"\w*.  
\v 17 Those \w who|strong="H5288"\w* carried \add baskets of supplies on their heads/shoulders\add* \w and|strong="H5288"\w* those \w who|strong="H5288"\w* built \w the|strong="H6584"\w* wall \w did|strong="H5288"\w* \w their|strong="H6584"\w* work \w with|strong="H4325"\w* one hand, \w and|strong="H5288"\w* held \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w weapon|strong="H7973"\w* \w with|strong="H4325"\w* \w the|strong="H6584"\w* other hand.  
\v 18 All those who were building \add the wall\add* had \w a|strong="H3068"\w* dagger fastened to their side. The man who would blow the trumpet \add if our enemies attacked\add* was standing at my side.   
\p
\v 19 Then I said to the officials, the other important men, and the other people, “This wall is very long, and \w we|strong="H3068"\w* are far apart from each other along the wall.  
\v 20 If you hear the man blowing the trumpet, gather around us at that place. \add Remember that\add* our God will fight for us!”   
\p
\v 21 So \w we|strong="H3068"\w* continued to work. Half of the men continued to hold their spears all day, from when the sun rose \add in the morning\add* until the stars appeared \add at night\add*.  
\v 22 At that time, I also said to the people, “Tell every worker and his helper that they must stay inside Jerusalem at night. By doing that, they can guard us at night, and they can work \add on the wall\add* during the daytime.”  
\v 23 During that time, none of us ever took off our clothes (\w OR|strong="H3068"\w*, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* wore our clothes all the time)—I and my relatives and my workers and the guards who were with me. And \w we|strong="H3068"\w* had our weapons with us, in our hands.   
\c 5  
\s1 Nehemiah helped the oppressed people  
\p
\v 1  \add Later,\add* \w many|strong="H1419"\w* \w of|strong="H5971"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* \w men|strong="H1419"\w* \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w their|strong="H1961"\w* wives protested \w loudly|strong="H1419"\w* \w about|strong="H1961"\w* what \add some of\add* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* \add other\add* \w Jews|strong="H3064"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* doing.  
\v 2 \w Some|strong="H7227"\w*/\w One|strong="H2421"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w them|strong="H3947"\w* said, “We \w have|strong="H3426"\w* \w many|strong="H7227"\w* \w children|strong="H1121"\w*. \w So|strong="H3947"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* need \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w grain|strong="H1715"\w* \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H3426"\w* able \w to|strong="H1121"\w* eat \w and|strong="H1121"\w* continue \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w live|strong="H2421"\w*.”   
\p
