\pi1
\v 43  \add Other\add* \w descendants|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w Levi|strong="H3881"\w* \w who|strong="H1121"\w* returned \w were|strong="H1121"\w*:  
\li2 74 from the clan of Jeshua and Kadmiel, who are descendants of Hodevah \add who is also known as Hodaviah\add*;   
