\pi1
\v 57 \w Descendants|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H5650"\w* \w servants|strong="H5650"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* King \w Solomon|strong="H8010"\w* \w who|strong="H1121"\w* returned \w were|strong="H1121"\w*:  
